Parton-level objects are defined for simulated events. Only top quarks decaying directly to a W boson and a b-quark in the simulation are considered.3 The full phase space for the measurements presented in this paper is defined by the set of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
