				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mu +$$\end{document}μ+jets channels give consistent results and are therefore combined by summing the event yields before the unfolding procedure.

